## 1. Workflow Overview

This document simulates the complete AI Live Action Studio pipeline for creating a live-action video adaptation of Solo Leveling Chapter 1 (Hospital Awakening scene). The workflow follows our established agent-based architecture:

```
MANGA INPUT
