[Scene Analyzer Agent] → Structured Scene Data
     ↓
[Character Manager Agent] → Consistent Character References
     ↓
[Environment Manager Agent] → Consistent Environment References
     ↓
[Cinematography Agent] → Shot List & Camera Plan
     ↓
[Prompt Builder Agent] → Generation Prompts for All Assets
     ↓
[Generation Agents] → Create Assets (Image, Video, Voice, Music, FX)
